text:
BROOOO!
Yaad hai mujhe abhi bhi, poore ek saal hum dono ka bhand hone k baad ek hi natak tha... video call karke ek dusre ko bt dena xD Bohot yaadein hai bhai apni toh sath me! Ramaiya, nainital, tera room, mera room, Nihal ka room, bhandi me na jaane kiska room har jagah daaru party ki hai apan ne. Kaafi time toh ho gya hai party kie hue, aa raha hu noida kuch dino me jamate kuch :p

Cheers to all the parties, many more to come! <3

Ayoo mere cheete mere sher! (cringe ho gya nahi?) Kaafi din aur kaafi raatein bakchodi me guzri hai apni, uss raat to chacha einstein ki kabr bhi hil gyi thi jab humne *ahem* *ahem*

Philosophy, physics, football pata nahi kitne common interests sath me cultivate kie hai apan ne. Ek interest fest ka bhi tha, alas online hi dekhna pada. But koi na bhai fest k time jab gand fati thi tab kaafi sath dia tune <3

Anyways you have been an integral part of my life throughout iitk ki journey, aage bhi milenge hi apan. Mumbai reh gaya yaar, but koi na ghoomne ka bahana bhi toh chahiye :') You've already covered a lot mere memoir me, I can't thank you enough for everything that you've done. Best of luck  bhai <3 <3
